snippet.title: MultiShadow1979
snippet.description:
"Know thyself, or be controlled by those who do." -Barbarossaa

"We don't like to admit it, but part of being a man is being alone.. we exist for ourselves and generally speaking, people don't give a shit about us.. unless we are doing something important, and then when we stop doing something important.. we aren't important anymore." -Stardusk

"For us, there is no spring. Just the wind that smells fresh before the storm." -Conan
